  "text": "SmEdA formulation is presented in details in [CITATION_1] . One gives here the outline of this formulation. First, it is based on the estimation of the energy sharing by two coupled modes from a relation established by Scharton and Lyon [CITATION_2] considering two oscillators excited by white noise forces and coupled by a spring and a gyroscopic element.",
